title: Recreation Information Database - RIDB
description: XML extractable listing of US Gov't Recreation sites
keyword: recreation, camping, hiking, visitor center, forest service, us army corps of engineers, national park service, bureau of reclamation, bureau of land management, fish and wildlife

title: US Forest Service Administrative Forest Boundaries
description: A map service displaying the area encompassing all the National Forest System lands administered by an unit. The area encompasses private lands, other governmental agency lands, and may contain National Forest System lands within the proclaimed boundaries of another administrative unit. All National Forest System lands fall within one and only one Administrative Forest Area.
keyword: Region, Forest Number, Forest Name, NFS Lands, USDA Forest Service, ALP Land Dataset, Land Status, US Forest Service, Forest Service, National Forest
organizationName: US Forest Service, Department of Agriculture
reasonBeingHighValue: Furthers the core mission of the agency
reasonBeingNew: This new map service makes the official Forest Service administrative forest boundaries available to the public and to other government agencies.

title: US Forest Service Ranger District Boundaries
description: A map service displaying the boundary that encompasses a Ranger District. This SDE Geodatabase is intended for read-only use. The purpose of the data is to provide display, identification, and analysis tools for determining current boundary information for Forest Service managers, GIS Specialists, and others. Symbolized with fill and outline Labeling turns on at larger scales Best available source with a target scale of 1:24000 for Continental U.S., Puerto Rico, and Hawaii and 1:63360 for Alaska.
keyword: Ranger Districts, Forest Name, District Number, District Name, NFS Lands, US Forest Service, ALP Land Dataset, Land Status, Forest Service, USDA Forest Service
organizationName: US Forest Service, Department of Agriculture
reasonBeingHighValue: Furthers the core mission of the agency
reasonBeingNew: This new map service makes the official Forest Service ranger district boundaries available to the public and to other government agencies.
